problem: i want to calulate sigma(i from r to n) C(i,r) , where C is a combination.
Solution: By Hockey-stick identity sigma(i from r to n) C(i,r) = C(n+1,r+1).
Link: https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Hockey-stick_identity?fbclid=IwAR1WGuoMKTngfNz9jWHksekHIUU0sZ_3hR6u1DlIM3qS40pZIcwIWvPEIWc
